\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.html#Lean.Lsp.instFromJsonRpcWireFormat.fromJson\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Lsp</span>.<span class=\"name\">instFromJsonRpcWireFormat</span>.<span class=\"name\">fromJson</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Json/Basic.html#Lean.Json\">Json</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Except\">Except</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.html#Lean.Lsp.RpcWireFormat\">RpcWireFormat</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.html#Lean.Lsp.instFromJsonRpcWireFormat.fromJson","kind":"def","line":53,"name":"Lean.Lsp.instFromJsonRpcWireFormat.fromJson","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.lean#L53-L53"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.html#Lean.Lsp.RpcWireFormat.v1\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Lsp</span>.<span class=\"name\">RpcWireFormat</span>.<span class=\"name\">v1</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.html#Lean.Lsp.RpcWireFormat\">RpcWireFormat</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Version `1` is like `0`,\nexcept that RPC references are serialized as `{\"__rpcref\": n}`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.html#Lean.Lsp.RpcWireFormat.v1","kind":"ctor","line":50,"name":"Lean.Lsp.RpcWireFormat.v1","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.lean#L50-L52"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.html#Lean.Lsp.RpcWireFormat.v0\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Lsp</span>.<span class=\"name\">RpcWireFormat</span>.<span class=\"name\">v0</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.html#Lean.Lsp.RpcWireFormat\">RpcWireFormat</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Version `0` uses JSON.\nSerialized RPC data is stored directly in `RpcCallParams.params` and in `JsonRpc.Response.result`\n(as opposed to being wrapped in additional metadata).\nGeneral types (except RPC references) are (de)serialized via `ToJson/FromJson`.\nRPC references are serialized as `{\"p\": n}`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.html#Lean.Lsp.RpcWireFormat.v0","kind":"ctor","line":44,"name":"Lean.Lsp.RpcWireFormat.v0","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.lean#L44-L49"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.html#Lean.Lsp.RpcWireFormat\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Lsp</span>.<span class=\"name\">RpcWireFormat</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The *RPC wire format* specifies how user data is encoded in RPC requests. ","docLink":"./Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.html#Lean.Lsp.RpcWireFormat","kind":"inductive","line":42,"name":"Lean.Lsp.RpcWireFormat","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.lean#L42-L53"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Server/Rpc/Basic.html#Lean.Lsp.instToStringRpcRef\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span 